text: Hey @UPS @UPSHelp, your motto is “What can brown do for you?” I’ll tell you what you guys can do...try knocking on my door so I’m actually AWARE that you are attempting a delivery. Yet again, I have missed ANOTHER package! What happened to taking care of the customer?!

@StefanieLucyyy I know how upsetting and frustrating this would be. Use this link to DM us the tracking number as well as your address and phone number so we may review this. ^CK https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ

@UPSHelp, yet another “attempt” has been made. But with true UPS fashion, NO KNOCKING. All this just to receive another call from my local facility saying “Nothing she can do and I have to wait til tomorrow.” 🤬🤬 this is a recurring problem I have at my home with UPS!
